  • public class FilterCriteriaDTO
extends DTO
    DTO expresses FilterCriteria. This data structure is used for searching resources.
    See Also:
    oneM2M TS-0004 6.3.5.8, oenM2M TS-0004 7.3.3.17.17
    "NotThreadSafe"
